Seahorse base Spark docker image with Kerberos
==============================================

The image contains Spark libraries required for running inside a docker container.
Can be used as a base image for applications requiring spark libraries.
Contains preinstalled Kerberos libs and programs, including ktinit.

1. Building the image

   $ docker build -t deepsense-spark-krb .

2. Running the image

   $ docker run -h sandbox -d deepsense-spark-krb
